title: ear cuff of the vampire bat
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While wearing this ceramic bat ear cuff, you can mentally command the cuff to enhance your hearing. When you do, the bat's eyes flash with a red glow as its ceramic fangs bite down on your ear. You suffer 1 [[harm]], and immediately gain a large [[advantage]] to attempts made to listen carefully for 1 minute.